In contrast , assuming that the cost of belief distortion is given by $C(\eta,\mu)=\mathrm{D_{KL}}(\eta||\mu)$ for any $\eta,\mu\in\mathopen[0,1\mathclose]$ , the optimal beliefs and behavior of a wishful Receiver are given by
\begin{equation}\label{eqn:belief_distortion_health}
